thingscrap.py : simple stupid thingiverse's thing scraper, leeching all thing's downloadable parts based on the thing ID (or maybe should work, but never tried..)

$ ./thingscrap.py 4148
fetching object 4148 (http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4148)
got thing "Prusa simplified mendel by prusajr", 8 parts
downloading belt-clamp.stl at prusa_simplified_mendel_by_prusajr-Thingiverse_4148/belt-clamp.stl
downloading bar-clamp.stl at prusa_simplified_mendel_by_prusajr-Thingiverse_4148/bar-clamp.stl
downloading x-carriage.stl at prusa_simplified_mendel_by_prusajr-Thingiverse_4148/x-carriage.stl
downloading coupling.stl at prusa_simplified_mendel_by_prusajr-Thingiverse_4148/coupling.stl
downloading y-slider-better.stl at prusa_simplified_mendel_by_prusajr-Thingiverse_4148/y-slider-better.stl
downloading z-motor-mount.stl at prusa_simplified_mendel_by_prusajr-Thingiverse_4148/z-motor-mount.stl
downloading x-end-idler.stl at prusa_simplified_mendel_by_prusajr-Thingiverse_4148/x-end-idler.stl
downloading x-end-motor.stl at prusa_simplified_mendel_by_prusajr-Thingiverse_4148/x-end-motor.stl

